module.description: This module provides a CSV file called 'HEALTH_STAT_Data_8cb42e4a-b2e4-43b2-b249-822aa18822ff.csv', which contains data on maternal mortality over time in OECD countries. There are five columns of data, with the last three of most interest: a country label, a year, and mortality (deaths per 1000 live births). This file was downloaded from the OECD's Stat Extracts service.
